    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nCurrently, `vim.pack` lockfile health checks don't recognize git `insteadOf` aliases as the same source as the expanded ones.\n<img width=\"833\" height=\"115\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b92a33bc-5d89-4dda-a9a1-6df3d35c4bc6\" />\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nEither implement git alias expansion here or maybe remove the check altogether? I don't know what would be better, honestly",
